name: Serenity Neural Interface
desc: A revolutionary neural interface that seamlessly integrates with the user's brain, providing enhanced cognitive capabilities and direct communication with compatible technologies.

name: Serenity Ocular Implants
desc: Ocular implants designed to enhance visual acuity and provide augmented reality overlays. It offers customizable display options, from reading assistance to dynamic information about the surrounding environment.

name: Serenity Adaptation Module
desc: Implants that enable users to adapt to different environmental conditions effortlessly. From extreme temperatures to varying atmospheric pressures, Serenity ensures users remain comfortable in any habitat.

name: Harmony Digestive Processor
desc: For individuals with digestive challenges, the Harmony assists in breaking down nutrients more efficiently. The implant regulates digestive enzymes, ensuring optimal nutrient absorption and minimizing discomfort.

name: Harmony Biometric Monitor
desc: A bionic heart implant that monitors and regulates the user's cardiovascular system. Harmony heart implant promotes overall well-being by adjusting heart rate, blood pressure, and oxygen levels based on the individual's activity and health status.

name: Harmony Leg Prosthesis
desc: A state-of-the-art prosthetic limb designed for maximum comfort and natural movement. It utilizes advanced materials and sensors to provide a seamless and adaptive experience, allowing users to regain a full range of motion.

name: Harmony Hand Prosthesis
desc: A state-of-the-art prosthetic limb designed for maximum comfort and natural movement. It utilizes advanced materials and sensors to provide a seamless and adaptive experience, allowing users to regain a full range of motion.

name: Harmony Cognitive Enhancer
desc: A non-invasive neural interface designed to enhance cognitive functions for everyday use. It assists users in memory retention, multitasking, and problem-solving without sacrificing the natural thought process.

name: Harmony Enhancement Implant
desc: A vocal enhancement implant for individuals with speech challenges. This implant helps users produce clear and natural speech, promoting effective communication and social interaction.
